'''Nerf-throwing''' was a sport that involved throwing [[Nerf/Legends|nerfs]] for distance or accuracy.

[[Jabrogg Thung]] was a [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] intergalactic champion in the sport, who then became wanted by the [[Galactic Humane Society]] for mortally injuring several nerfs. They placed a 2,000 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credit]] [[Bounty/Legends|bounty]] on his head&mdash;[[Death/Legends|dead]] or alive.

